>

Ah; you're talking about httpunit!

Hmmm... And I see that you've posted your question to the
appropriate news group for that project, but have not received any
responses.

I see that the HTML processing was "improved" in httpunit 1.5.
(Apparently "improved" applies to everyone except you. For you,
it's "broken." ;-)

I still think the sourceforge httpunit-develop list is your best
bet. I'd bug them again.

You might post a link to your question(s) with a brief summary here:
http://www.c2.com/cgi/wiki?HttpUnit
(But it might not help either.)
